Simple Battery Capacity Tester using Sparkfun Arduino Pro Micro and 32x128 SSD1306 OLED screen

PINS connections :
  SSD1306 Oled Display
    SDA -> PIN2
    SCK -> PIN3

You can access the menu when discharge is off by clicking (shortclick) the pushbutton.
Navigate in menu using discharge button on/off to go down/up and 1 click to go up or down depending on the On/Off state, longpress to select item in menu
